Package: DROMA.Meta
Title: Drug Response and Omics Multi-step Meta Workflow
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-15
Authors@R:
    person("Peng Yu", "Zhong", email = "yc47680@um.edu.mo", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: DROMA.Meta wraps a four-step biomarker discovery workflow across
    preclinical, TCGA concordance, and clinical validation stages. It provides
    helpers for valid drug and tumor-type filtering, TCGA Anderson-Darling
    concordance checks, and script-driven execution over drug and tumor-type
    combinations as an application package built on DROMA.R.
